headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Alliant Energy (LNT) After Its Steady Multi‑Year Share Price Climb
summary: If you are wondering whether Alliant Energy at around US$71.63 is offering fair value or whether you might be paying up for stability in a regulated utility, this article is designed to help you put a clear price tag on the stock. The share price has recently closed at US$71.63, with returns of 0.7% over 7 days, 7.2% over 30 days, 9.2% year to date, 16.0% over 1 year, 54.8% over 3 years and 78.8% over 5 years.
